name: Moneyplex Export
query:
SELECT
-- `tabPayment Request`.company AS "Kontoname",
`tabPayment Request`.bank_account_no AS "Kontonummer:Data:150",
`tabPayment Request`.branch_code AS "Bankleitzahl:Data:80",
`tabPayment Request`.transaction_date AS "Datum:Date:100",
-- `tabPayment Request`.valuta AS "Valuta",
-- `tabPayment Request`.supplier_name AS "Name",
`tabPayment Request`.party_type AS "Party Type:Data:80",
`tabPayment Request`.party AS "Party:Data:120",
`tabPayment Request`.iban AS "Iban:Data:200",
`tabPayment Request`.swift_number AS "BIC/SWIFT:Data:80",
`tabPayment Request`.reference_name AS "Zweck:Data:120",
`tabPayment Request`.mode_of_payment AS "Kategorie:Data:100",
`tabPayment Request`.grand_total AS "Betrag:Currency:120",
`tabPayment Request`.currency AS "Währung:Data:60"
FROM
`tabPayment Request`
WHERE
`tabPayment Request`.docstatus = 0
